summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to Land Use and Zoning; amending Plat 53W, Page 134 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone certain property located on or near the south side of Admiral Way, generally between 59th Avenue Southwest and 64th Avenue Southwest, from Lowrise 2 (L-2) to Single Family 5000 (SF 5000) Zoning. (Petition of Sharon Gustafson, et al., C.F. 29600.)
